        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>ICH Score</th>\n<th>Mortality Rate</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>13%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>26%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>72%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>97%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>100%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6*</td>\n<td>100%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*No patients in study score 6, but estimates 100%</p>",
